# Summary
This documentation explains how to deploy recommendation models in personalization campaigns using Amplitude's Profile API, including authentication, request parameters, response interpretation, and integration steps, as well as how to analyze recommendation performance through the Performance tab with metrics like lift against baseline and statistical significance.

